folder: Fresh Pond Road & 60th Drive, Queens, NY
text:
Fresh Pond Road, at 60th Drive, showing the surrounding area before it was developed. Note the old frame dwellings on the left and rows of new brick houses in the right background.
M.4 -22-~NS
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection  About 1922

folder: Fresh Pond Road & 60th Drive, Queens, NY
text:
Fresh Pond Rd. (center of view), north from about 60th Drive, showing in the center of view the Richard Way house located at the S.W. corner of 59th Drive and Fresh Pond Road. This low peaked roof structure was
not in existence in 1929.
1922.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
